title: Happy Hour #31: Freeland Spirits
itunes:title: Happy Hour #31: Freeland Spirits
description:
Anney and Samantha have a spirited (#sorrynotsorry) discussion about the power of legacy for women, what that looks like in our history and what we hope it looks like in our future while sipping on cocktails made with Freeland Spirits.
